thread.title: Wildfires may spark higher premiums, non-renewals for homeowners
thread.title_full: Wildfires may spark higher premiums, non-renewals for homeowners - San Francisco Chronicle

author: Kathleen Pender
title: Wildfires may spark higher premiums, non-renewals for homeowners
text: Some Californians could pay more for homeowners insurance or have their policies not renewed as a result of wildfires that swept the state this summer, state Insurance Commissioner Dave Jones said last week.
